ulations cannot be interpreted as connectivity, since it is\nin general incorrect to associate an extracranial electrode or sensor to the\nunderlying cortex.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jun 2007 19:48:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2007 11:35:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2007 12:24:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-07-12"}
