 methodology able to evaluate\nthe seismic risk in the regions with similar geological conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jun 2007 06:09:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jun 2007 04:42:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-06-14"}
